{
  "stem": "19939.4",
  "chunk_idx": 12,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And every time a German-- you know, they would came representative from the railroad, you know, from Krakow, I was sent to wait on them.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The dining room was upstairs.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "The same thing-- the Polish girls didn't want, you go, right?",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So I brought him his tray, this SS, right, look straight into his eyes.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And he said in German, danke, Fraulein-- you know, thank you, miss.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Another one, some wanted to give me a tip.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And so this fear, you know, was accumulating, accumulating, right?",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And then I wanted how to escape.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Because I felt this is already-- the fire is already under my feet.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And the Americans landed already in Italy.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "How did you know that?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Because we had a radio.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We had the German-- you know, they had the radio.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "The other girls, too, we were cleaning upstairs, the dining rooms, the something.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I heard all this news, the BBC.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "You know, we just did.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 83,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I knew about the Americans.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 83,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "There were papers, too, right.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 83,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But they didn't say anything.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 83,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I didn't know anything what was going in Africa or nothing.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 83,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So I thought that they will see-- there were many instances that were just on the brink of being discovered.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 83,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But let's, let's return to that.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 84,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "To that.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 85,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 86,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "That had not only a major effect.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 86,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I already planned how to further escape.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 86,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I cannot stay here anymore.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 86,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Because it's getting bad.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 86,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Now the, the Austrians and Germans, they had the right to ask for help, slave work, right?",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 86,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And they were allowed, because all these slave workers that went to Germany went to work in the fields or factories, I mean, whatever, right?",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 86,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And there was one man that I knew him being from the Alp, from Tyrol.",
      "word_count": 15
    }
  ],
